snippet.title: CATS REACT TO AMBER HEARD LYING ON THE STAND!🙀 Depp vs Heard REACTION #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
snippet.description:
In this Depp vs Heard reaction, my cats react to some Day 16 footage from the defamation lawsuit taking place in Fairfax County Circuit Court in Virginia. It was day 2 of Amber Heard testifying in the case AKA lying on the stand! This is how my cats reacted to the Amber Heard performance of a lifetime fake crying sham of a testimony

#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #DeppvsHeardTrial
